.TH "dwc3_alloc_one_event_buffer" 9 "dwc3_alloc_one_event_buffer" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
dwc3_alloc_one_event_buffer \- Allocates one event buffer structure
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "struct dwc3_event_buffer *" dwc3_alloc_one_event_buffer
.BI "(struct dwc3 *dwc "  ","
.BI "unsigned length "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "dwc" 12
Pointer to our controller context structure
.IP "length" 12
size of the event buffer
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Returns a pointer to the allocated event buffer structure on success
otherwise ERR_PTR(errno).
